name: BleedingAtNonCriticalSite
title: Bleeding at Non Critical Site
description: The intent of the measure that this SNOMED CT value set was created for is focused on non-critical site bleeding that has an etiology of medication-related bleeding, specifically Venous Thromboembolism Pharmacoprophylaxis medications.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this SNOMED CT value set is to identify non-critical site bleeding events during an encounter.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element related to Diagnosis.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes SNOMEDCT concepts that represent diagnoses that indicate a new onset of non-critical site bleeding of any kind.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that represent any diagnoses which may not always result in non-critical site bleeding. Injury or traumatic causes of bleeding should be excluded. Obstetric related bleeds are also excluded.)
